name: Over the Rainbow
overview: Can Alex color all the cubes without getting bonked by the gumdrops? Will he be vaporized by Grody the Witch or bit by Buzzbat? Watch out, Eraser Rabbit is stealing your colors, and Croak the Frog is smashing your cubes! Escape on a cloud...and melt Grody with rain. Then zap Buzzbat with a bolt of lightning.
